Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.60,0:21:04.87,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,快哭出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.56,0:21:07.04,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,青苹果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.68,0:21:10.96,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,紧抱在胸怀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.71,0:21:14.96,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,摔倒 逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.64,0:21:18.92,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,盯着狭小的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:26.76,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,谁愿意顺从地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.67,0:21:33.97,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,等待命运成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.58,0:21:39.50,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,千之风（不断挣扎）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.62,0:21:43.56,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,吹吧吹吧（嘶喊着）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.56,0:21:47.54,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是（即便如此）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.54,0:21:51.56,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,脆弱之泡沫（依然坚信）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.56,0:21:55.55,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,无法预测（上浮）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.55,0:21:59.61,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,向风暴（下沉）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:03.55,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,做抗争（即便如此）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.55,0:22:07.48,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,脆弱之泡沫（依旧独活）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.66,0:22:10.43,ED_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,破裂的瞬间
